data.name: TablePageStyle
desc: represents a page style for a spreadsheet.
This service extends the service com.sun.star.style.PageStyle with spreadsheet specific properties.
**since**
OOo 2.0

properties.name: CenterHorizontally
desc: determines whether the table is centered horizontally on the page.

properties.name: CenterVertically
desc: determines whether the table is centered vertically on the page.

properties.name: FirstPageNumber
desc: contains the page number applied to the first page for this sheet.
The value 0 indicates that the page numbers are continued from the previous sheet.

properties.name: LeftPageFooterContent
desc: contains the content of the footer for left pages.
After changing the footer text contents, this property has to be reinserted into the property set.

properties.name: LeftPageHeaderContent
desc: contains the content of the header for left pages.
After changing the header text contents, this property has to be reinserted into the property set.

properties.name: PageScale
desc: contains the scaling factor (in percent) for printing the sheet.

properties.name: PrintAnnotations
desc: enables printing of cell annotations.

properties.name: PrintCharts
desc: enables printing of charts.

properties.name: PrintDownFirst
desc: specifies the print order for the pages within each sheet.

If TRUE, the order for printing pages begins with top-to-bottom, then continues with the next set of cell columns to the right. If FALSE, the order for printing pages begins with left-to-right, then continues with the next set of cell rows to the bottom.

properties.name: PrintDrawing
desc: enables printing of drawing objects.

properties.name: PrintFormulas
desc: enables printing of formulas instead of their results.

properties.name: PrintGrid
desc: enables printing of the cell grid.

properties.name: PrintHeaders
desc: enables printing of column and row headers.

properties.name: PrintObjects
desc: enables printing of embedded objects.

properties.name: PrintZeroValues
desc: enables printing of zero-values.

properties.name: RightPageFooterContent
desc: contains the content of the footer for right pages.
After changing the footer text contents, this property has to be reinserted into the property set.

properties.name: RightPageHeaderContent
desc: contains the content of the header for right pages.
After changing the header text contents, this property has to be reinserted into the property set.

properties.name: ScaleToPages
desc: contains the number of pages the sheet will printed.

properties.name: ScaleToPagesX
desc: contains the number of horizontal pages the sheet will printed on.
**since**
OOo 2.0

properties.name: ScaleToPagesY
desc: contains the number of vertical pages the sheet will printed on.
**since**
OOo 2.0
